race.comment: LITTLE FELLA (8) hasn't put a hoof wrong saluting in both starts to date and Jones stays on top following that last-start Doomben victory. Can continue the picket fence here. ROYAL MOVER (3) finished behind the top selection at his latest effort in his first time tasting defeat. Should be right there at the business end again. GRAFTERBURNERS (1) wasn't disgraced at Group 1 level before the spell and will find this assignment much more to his liking. In the mix. CHAMPAGNE LANE (4) has won both starts in lesser grade but it's hard to knock winning form. Impossible to ignore. HI BARBIE (7) best of the rest while fresh.
